## Dataset

- **Dataset Name:** Bank Customer Churn Dataset  
- **Source:** [Kaggle - Bank Customer Churn Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/shubhammeshram579/bank-customer-churn-prediction)  
- **Rows:** 10,000  
- **Columns:** 12 (demographic, financial, and behavioral features)  
- **Target Variable:**  
  - `0` → Customer stayed  
  - `1` → Customer churned  

**Key Features:**  
- CustomerId, Geography, Gender, Age, Tenure  
- Balance, Credit Score, Number of Products  
- Has Credit Card, Is Active Member, Estimated Salary  
- Exited (Churn indicator)  

 
